,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:43:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底立法會有乜用</blockquote><br />\n出糧比議員。完。"},{"pid":"5741524ac5afda7cd259752e867fefb86c0797ab","tid":493304,"uid":21636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:45:34.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"6d770cbf94c9818c0bce86c92face2d40ba1c475","tid":493304,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d703b8c6d9c092140c236ad3d8a2c0c5016f735","tid":493304,"uid":3180,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"香港根本就唔係行民主制度<br />\n<br />\n政治角力弱勢個陣要拉布，泛民/獨立候選人攞幾多議席都係變相拎黎打飛機用<br />\n<br />\n一到表決日梗有啲人失蹤賣香港，今時今日選舉失利個啲真係無得怪香港人，根本老屎忽文化係香港議會制度失敗主因，有理想個啲無資源要籌旗，屎忽生上腦個啲就好控制可以扶搖直上"},{"pid":"79079f68767828aa5a1c39a929b81182ea75125a","tid":493304,"uid":111253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:53:25.000Z","msg":"立法會直接變做港區人大算啦"},{"pid":"3bb6ccbf88db69b5dc4eca476e706fb51304ecfa","tid":493304,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法定人數好似關基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家係改全體委員會法定人數，唔係大會法定人數。建制派認為基本法只係限制大會法定人數，而唔包括全體委員會。"},{"pid":"0dbb561dae604b595f4b374bbf59d7168a39b3ca","tid":493304,"uid":7068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T12:18:39.000Z","msg":"推"}]}